  <section id="overview">
    <h2>Application Overview</h2>
    <p>Break Catch is an extension that predicts bugs in your code, prior to launching your website. This is done through learning your historical data and patterns, so that you can prevent having to go back and repair code if something breaks on your first deployment.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="technology">
    <h2>Technology Overview</h2>
